member.name: TsActiveSelEnd
member.summary: Elements of the TsActiveSelEnd enumeration specify which end of a text store selection is active.

member.name: TsActiveSelEnd.TS_AE_NONE
member.summary: The selection has no active end. This is typical for all selections other than the default selection.

member.name: TsActiveSelEnd.TS_AE_START
member.summary: The active end of the selection is at the start of the range of text.

member.name: TsActiveSelEnd.TS_AE_END
member.summary: The active end of the selection is at the end of the range of text.
